8/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-5-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073718/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-5-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073718/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-5-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>What’s impressive about this setup is the gearing…it’s not a big cassette or compact chainring setup. And he was running deeper 50mm wheels!</p><p>His kit was a POC Octal helmet,&nbsp;Oakley Flight Jacket Prizm Road sunglasses,&nbsp;X-Bionic bibshorts with Assos and Gore jerseys (changed mid ride) with a Dryarn base layer underneath and Gore Windstopper vest over top. And Assos’ chamois cream to prevent chafing.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3.jpg\" alt=\"gabriele boassa everesting bike build details\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/03073707/gabriele-boassa-everesting-bike-build-spec-3-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><h3>Food and Nutrition for Everesting</h3><p>And here’s what he ate:</p><ul><li>12 rice cake</li><li>12 mini sandwich (ham, cream cheese, honey, etc)</li><li>Gel</li><li>Rce dish after 10h</li><li>1 litre water each hour</li><li>6 coke</li><li>3 red Bull</li><li>3 Mars candy bars</li><li>Caffeine gel and gum</li></ul><p>If Boasso’s name sounds familiar, it’s because he’s sent us component renderings in the past, like <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/05/20/concept-componentsbikedesign-shows-modular-three-piece-stem-seatpost-clamp-w-co2-storage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this modular stem design</a> and CO2-carrying seatpost collar. Huge thanks to him for sharing his story and bike spec.</p></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b77ec54d319a3dbaf749c8b38fa3cb5a92bacf137c53ed9fd66e2499784635a1","category":"Cycling"}